public Object getPropertyEntryValue(PropertyEntry entry) { if (entry == null) return null; Object o = props.get(PROP_HAS_PROPERTY_ENTRY); if (!(o instanceof List)) return null; List entries = (List) o; for (int i = 0; i < entries.size(); ++i) { Object other = entries.get(i); if (entry.equals(other)) { return ((PropertyEntry)entries.get(i)).getValue(); } } return null; }
